All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AppConfig
AppConfig extends the Configuration class allowing us to define our own configuration
AppService
AppService is the base class that starts the server.
DataManagerException
DataManagerException class is an extension of Exception and it is responsible for providing an error message when an exception related to the InventoryDataManager in thrown.
DummyDataGenerator
The DummyDataGenerator class is a utility class that can create patients and healthchecks in order to start the demo with already some patients and healthchecks to work with via the RESTful API.
HealthCheckCreationRequest
HealthCheckCreationRequest is a DTO class (Data Transfer Object) that allows clients to only have access to certain attributes when creating a new healthceck.
HealthCheckDescriptor
HealthCheckDescriptor is a classic POJO class that describes the structure of a healthcheck.
HealthCheckReadRequest
HealthCheckReadRequest is a DTO class (Data Transfer Object) that allows clients not to see null values of HealthCheckDescriptor's fields in response to a GET request.
HealthCheckResource
HealthCheckResource class contains a series of methods necessary for the correct management of incoming requests by a client, in accordance with the CRUD manipulation of the healthcheck resource.
HealthCheckUpdateRequest
HealthCheckUpdateRequest is a DTO class (Data Transfer Object) that allows clients to only have access to certain attributes when updating a healthceck.
IInventoryDataManager
IInventoryDataManager is an interface that is implemented in this project by InventoryDataManager.
InfoMessageDescriptorSS
InfoMessageDescriptorSS is a classic POJO class representing smartwatch info data.
InventoryDataManager
InventoryDataManager is a class implementation of IInventoryDataManager interface.
MqttConfigurationParametersSS
MqttConfigurationParametersSS is a utility class that provides configuration data to manage MQTT communication.
MqttHandler
MqttHandler is the class responsible for managing the MQTT communication, so it is the hook for the telemetry part of the complete project.
PatientCreationRequest
PatientCreationRequest is a DTO class (Data Transfer Object) that allows clients to only have access to certain attributes when creating a new patient.
PatientDescriptor
PatientDescriptor is a classic POJO class that describes the structure of a patient.
PatientResource
PatientResource class contains a series of methods necessary for the correct management of incoming requests by a client, in accordance with the CRUD manipulation of the patient resource.
PatientUpdateRequest
PatientUpdateRequest is a DTO class (Data Transfer Object) that allows clients to only have access to certain attributes when updating a patient.
SenMLPack
SenMLPack class represents a SenMLRecord ArrayList used for receiving telemetry data within MqttHandler and HealthCheckResource classes, and to emulate telemetry data within DummyDataGenerator
SenMLRecord
SenMLRecord class provides standardized structure for telemetry data
UtilityClass
UtilityClass is a helper class with only static methods that are useful in certain part of the codebase.
